OL,3,CShop hit with court order to close
OL,4,Cover mice infestation
OL,6,FA shop was ordered by a court to close
OL,7,Fafter defying an agreement to cease
OL,8,Ftrading until it dealt with a mouse
OL,9,Finfestation.
OL,11,FLatik, on Hessle Road in Hull, was
OL,12,Finitially found to have a rodent
OL,13,Fproblem during a routine visit by
OL,14,Fcouncil inspectors.
OL,16,FThey found droppings on the floor and
OL,17,Fshelves, along with opened packets of
OL,18,Fchewed food.
