OL,3,CShop hit with court order to close
OL,4,Cover mice infestation
OL,6,FThe shop was deemed an imminent risk
OL,7,Fto public health, and the owner signed
OL,8,Fan agreement to close until the
OL,9,Finfestation had been dealt with and
OL,10,Fapproved by an officer.
OL,12,FBut it was found to be trading as
OL,13,Fnormal during a follow-up visit.
OL,15,FThere was further evidence of food
OL,16,Fthat had been chewed and covered in
OL,17,Fdroppings, as well as out-of-date food
OL,18,Fitems.
