OL,3,CShop hit with court order to close
OL,4,Cover mice infestation
OL,6,FCouncil officers issued an emergency
OL,7,Fprohibition notice, which was
OL,8,Fconverted to an emergency prohibition
OL,9,Forder at Hull Magistrates Court.
OL,11,FViolating the order is a criminal
OL,12,Foffence.
OL,14,FThe shop has now been able to open
OL,15,Fagain, after proving the building had
OL,16,Fbeen thoroughly pest-proofed and deep
OL,17,Fcleaned.
