OL,3,CShop hit with court order to close
OL,4,Cover mice infestation
OL,6,FCllr Julia Conner, of Hull City
OL,7,FCouncil whose portfolio includes
OL,8,Fenvironmental health, said: "Our teams
OL,9,Falways do what they can to work with
OL,10,Fbusiness owners and operators to
OL,11,Fensure they understand why action is
OL,12,Fbeing taken, and what they must do.
OL,13,FUnfortunately, if restrictions are
OL,14,Fviolated, sometimes further action is
OL,15,Fnecessary.
