OL,3,CShop hit with court order to close
OL,4,Cover mice infestation
OL,6,F"This showed a clear disregard for the
OL,7,Fhealth and safety of customers,
OL,8,Fputting those who were unknowingly
OL,9,Fusing the shop at risk. Incidents like
OL,10,Fthis are why routine checks are so
OL,11,Fimportant.
OL,13,FAfter being cleaned and approved by an
OL,14,Fofficer, the shop has now been allowed
OL,15,Fto reopen.
